:586,tag:32,tagName:Geographic Location,name:Seoul,helpText:null},{id:4461,tag:32,tagName:Geographic Location,name:South Korea,helpText:null},{id:175,tag:10,tagName:Relationship Types,name:Friends,helpText:null},{id:203,tag:12,tagName:Setting,name:Big City,helpText:null},{id:32,tag:2,tagName:Sub-Genre,name:Adaptation,helpText:null},{id:126,tag:5,tagName:Time Period,name:2020s,helpText:null},{id:199,tag:12,tagName:Setting,name:Alternate Reality,helpText:null}]","lists":[],"translations":{"nameTranslations":[{"name":"전지적 독자 시점","language":"kor","IsPrimary":true},{"name":"Omniscient Reader: The Prophecy","language":"eng","IsPrimary":false},{"name":"The Prophet: Omniscient Reader","language":"pt","IsPrimary":false},{"name":"全知读者视角","language":"zho","IsPrimary":false},{"name":"อ่านชะตาวันสิ้นโลก","tagline":"จากคนอ่านนิยายกลายเป็นผู้พลิกชะตาโลก","language":"tha","IsPrimary":false}],"overviewTranslations":[{"overview":"동명 웹소설을 원작으로 한 ‘전지적 독자 시점’은 어느 날 자신이 읽던 소설의 내용대로 바뀌어 버린 세계에서 주인공 김독자가 세상을 구하려 하면서 벌어지는 일을 그린 작품.","language":"kor","IsPrimary":true},{"overview":"Dok-ja was an average office worker whose sole interest was reading his favorite web novel 'Three Ways to Survive the Apocalypse.' But when the novel suddenly becomes reality, he is the only person who knows how the world will end. Armed with this realization, Dok-ja uses his understanding to change the course of the story, and the world, as he knows it.","language":"eng","IsPrimary":false},{"overview":"Dokja era um funcionário de escritório que só se interessava em ler a web novel favorita dele, Três Maneiras de Sobreviver ao Apocalipse.\r\n\r\nQuando a história se torna realidade, Dokja é a única pessoa que sabe como o mundo vai acabar.\r\n\r\nEle usa o seu conhecimento para mudar o curso da história e do mundo.\r\n\r\nThe Prophet: Omniscient Reader é uma adaptação do webtoon Omniscient Reader's Viewpoint de Sing Shong, que foi publicado entre 2018 e 2020.","language":"pt","IsPrimary":false},{"overview":"平凡上班族金独子（安孝燮 饰），唯一嗜好是阅读网络小说《在灭亡的世界中存活的三种方法》，不过在长达十年的连载期间，他却是这个小说的唯一读者。当金独子在地铁车厢读完小说最终话时，小说中的场景却转瞬成为现实。地铁车厢仿佛成为人间炼狱，巨大怪物正践踏着这座城市，以及凭空出现在眼前的讯息：“您收到了第一个主线任务。”紧接着，熟悉的小说角色纷纷登场，而那个无比强大、牵动着整个世界命运的小说主角刘众赫（李敏镐 饰），开始照着剧情一一行动。眼看熟悉的世界将不复返，一个崭新的世界正在诞生，身为唯一知晓这个新世界结局的金独子，将在升级自身能力的同时，打造出与原本小说截然不同的结局。","language":"zho","IsPrimary":false},{"overview":"นวนิยายเรื่องโปรดของ ด็อกจา กลายมาเป็นลางบอกเหตุของเหตุการณ์ที่จะเกิดขึ้นจริง เขาจึงใช้ความรู้อันยากที่จะเข้าใจเกี่ยวกับเรื่องราวหายนะวันสิ้นโลกที่กำลังจะเกิดขึ้นดังกล่าว ในฐานะของพนักงานบริษัทที่จะเปลี่ยนแปลงโชคชะตาของโลกใบนี้","tagline":"จากคนอ่านนิยายกลายเป็นผู้พลิกชะตาโลก","language":"tha","IsPrimary":false}],"aliases":"[Omniscient Reader Viewpoint,Omniscient Reader: The Prophet,Omniscient Reader]"},"companies":{"studio":[],"network":[],"production":[{"id":26508,"name":"Lotte Entertainment","slug":"lotte-entertainment","country":"kor","primaryCompanyType":3,"companyType":{"companyTypeId":3,"companyTypeName":"Production Company"},"parentCompany":{"relation":{}}}],"distributor":[],"special_effects":[]},"production_countries":[{"id":282791,"country":"kor","name":"South Korea"}],"inspirations":["{id:40451,type:3,type_name:Book,url:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43802732}"],"spoken_languages":"[kor]","first_release":{"country":"kor","date":"2025-07-23"}}